    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_003/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "Card focuses narrowly on the CCS bias correction component of MobiLipid workflow. Paper scope is broader: it describes the entire MobiLipid tool including library creation, benchmarking, and correction. The card's focus is a valid subtask within the paper's scope.",
        "Card does not mention the U13C-labeled lipid library or internal standardization strategy, which are central to how MobiLipid performs correction. The correction functions depend on this library as reference."
