      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The candidate card frames the task as an investigative analysis of 'minimum lipids-per-class requirement,' but the paper presents 3 as an established minimum and demonstrates its application rather than deriving it empirically.",
        "The expected outputs suggest a systematic parametric study (quality metrics as a function of lipid count), but the paper's analysis is presented as an exemplary application to one dataset (TIM-MS yeast extract) with post-hoc inspection of correction function performance.",
