      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "After curation using these stringent criteria, the new MobiLipid library contains 377 DTCCSN2 values for 162 U13C-labeled lipids detected at lipid species level across 15 lipid classes (AcCa, acylcarnitine; Cer, ceramide; Co, coenzyme; DG, diacylglycerol; HexCer, hexosylceramide; LPC, lysophosphatidylcholine; LPE, lysophosphatidylethanolamine; PA, phosphatidic acid; PC, phosphatidylcholine; PE, phosphatidylethanolamine; PG, phosphatidylglycerol; PI, phosphatidylinositol; PS, phosphatidylserine; SPH, sphingoid base; TG, triacylglycerol)",
      "asbval:note": null,
