      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Align detected ion mobility-mass spectrometry lipid features to a curated reference library (DT CCS N2) by matching mass-to-charge and retention time identifiers, enabling quantitative bias assessment and correction of collision cross section (CCS) values against theoretical refe",
