      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms R and RStudio are used for data processing and visualization, but does not explicitly name ggplot2, data.table, or DT packages. The paper uses Skyline 23.1.0.268 for targeted lipidomics data processing and PNNL PreProcessor for demultiplexing, not the specific R packages claimed.",
