      "asbval:evidence_quote": "the new MobiLipid library contains 377 DTCCSN2 values for 162 U13C-labeled lipids detected at lipid species level across 15 lipid classes... only DTCCSN2 values fulfilling the following criteria were included: (1) high mass accuracy (\u22645 ppm error), (2) confirmed detection in at least two samples, (3) confirmed coelution of adducts, and (4) a CCS relative standard deviation <1%.",
